; Task 3: Flashcard App - Main Program Loop (Full 24 Cards)
;
; This is the complete flashcard application that:
; 1. Selects a random flashcard (0-23) from all 24 European capitals
; 2. Displays the question
; 3. Waits for ANY keypress from the user
; 4. Displays the answer
; 5. Repeats with a new random card
;
; All 24 flashcards are included and fully functional.
; Keyboard input: Press any key to reveal the answer.

(jump program-start)

